apps.localizedDescription:
uYouPlusExtra is a modified version of uYouPlus with some extra features (requires iOS 14.0 and later).
Full infomation about uYouPlus (uYou+) is available on Github: https://github.com/qnblackcat/uYouPlus/

Credits: Please keep the Credits if you re-up uYouPlus! https://github.com/qnblackcat/uYouPlus#credits

Attention:
- If you like the app, considering support the developers!
- YTUHD is not stable atm. You might encounter stuttering, heat, battery drain..., especially when playing at 2160p (4K) quality. However, this should not happen if you use TrollStore.
- Unless you're using TrollStore, deep-link (aka Open in the YouTube App) simply will not work.

Known issues:
- uYou's issues: https://github.com/MiRO92/uYou-for-YouTube/issues
- uYouPlus's issues: https://github.com/qnblackcat/uYouPlus

apps.versionDescription:
RELEASE F1: (June 1st 2023)

- Updated YouTube from v18.20.3 to v18.21.3
- Updated YTNoModernUI (arichorn)
- Added “16.42.3” YouTube Version
- Added Red Progress Bar
- Added Old Buffer Bar
- Updated LowContrastMode (arichorn)
- Added UILabel Support
- Added ASyncDisplayKit Support

uYou Fixes
- Fix stretched artwork in uYou's player view (therealFoxster)
- Fix crash on startup after closing with uYou download in progress (therealFoxster)
- Disabled DontEatMyContent Tweak
- Tweak has been disabled for this releases due to issues with the v1.0.6 release - will return hopefully next release.
